{"type":null,"faqId":13028,"title":"H30-L01&H30-L02手机待机时间短，耗电快，如何解决？","answer":"<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;font-size:8pt;\"><span>l</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>开启省电模式：进入<b>设置</b>界面，点击<b>省电管理</b>，根据需要选择省电模式为<b>智能省电</b>或<b>超级省电</b>。</span></span> \n</p>\n<img style=\"width:609px;height:361px;\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=37704\" width=\"609\" height=\"394\" /> \n<p>\n\t&nbsp;\n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;font-size:8pt;\"><span>l</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>清理后台暂不使用的应用程序。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;font-size:8pt;\"><span>l</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>缩短屏幕待机时间。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;font-size:8pt;\"><span>l</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>降低屏幕亮度。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;font-size:8pt;\"><span>l</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>降低音量。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;font-size:8pt;\"><span>l</span></span><span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">不使用移动网络、蓝牙、</span><span>WLAN </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">或</span><span> GPS </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">时，请关闭对应功能。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>华为会定期在官网发布最新软件版本，以优化软件性能，请您及时升级手机，以体验更好的手机性能。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>若您认为手机待机时间过短，已影响正常使用，请联系客服或携带购机发票前往服务网点检修。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span>* </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">图示仅供参考，具体操作请以手机实际界面为准。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span></span></span>&nbsp;\n</p>","faqTypeId":133,"faqType":"电池与充电","useful":1,"unUseful":2,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"4007","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Battery-Charging","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","pr